title: Alternote 1.0.9 [MAC OS X]
description:

Alternote is a gorgeous OS X note-taking app that integrates with Evernote. Designed to be the most convenient and natural way to make notes, collect information, write down your ideas, feelings and memories. Alternote is totally secure. There are no Alternote servers in the chain, just you, your Mac, and Evernote backend.

What's new in version 1.0.9:
- A lot of fixes and improvements in attachments management and sync.
- Fix bold and italic keyboard shortcut.
- Fix empty settings pane on the first launch.
- Fix cropped letters when printing a note or saving to PDF.
- Performance improvements.
